node.text:
If you haven’t heard this radio transmission, please take the time to listen. ⛔️Be cautioned it is hard to listen to.⛔️

The calm voice in the chaos  in Chicago during the incident that occurred on 8/7/2021. Thank you Dispatcher Keith Thornton - The way he took control of this incident and talked to his officers, kept his air completely shut down and clear, set a perimeter within seconds quite possibly is what resulted in the apprehension of the suspects. 

Dispatcher Keith Thornton was fast thinking and took initiative without any direction in the very beginning stages and ran the emergency like an actual incident commander - far beyond the criteria of any dispatcher. 

The world heard you loud and clear and we stand with you. 💙🖤💙🖤💙🖤💙
#chicago #dispatcherlife #policedispatcher #bluelivesmatter #chicagopolicedepartment #keiththorton #policeofficer #police #lawenforcement

After COVID-Stricken Migrants Seen ‘Coughing, Sneezing’ at a Restaurant. 

HIDALGO COUNTY, Texas (CBSDFW.COM) – The La Joya Police Department issued a public health announcement after an officer approached an undocumented migrant family at Whataburger who told him Border Patrol released them because they had COVID-19.

On July 26 the police department of the small town along the Rio Grande and Mexican border shared details of the incident. They said a concerned citizen at the restaurant waved down the officer. The citizen told him about the family “coughing and sneezing without covering their mouths and not wearing face masks.” Whataburger management also told the officer that they wanted the group to leave as well due to “their disregard to other people’s health.”

You can tell that there is/was some type of business negotiation happening or already happened between the police officers and the human smugglers, because they ask who put the finger? (Who told on us ~ then mention some type of raid, but it’s hard to understand)

Do not know if the police officers walked away from this as the video ends here. 

Hopefully the @pncdeguatemala PNC Police of Guatemala will look into this if they haven’t already. 

“Se nota que ahí hay negocio entre la PNC y los polleros, porque pregunta quién puso el dedo (se entiende que por una redada) y por eso no se defienden los policías, además se nota que hay un par de mexicanos. Los negocios de la PNC en todo el interior ojalá investiguen!!”

node.text:
Democrats are now rewarding non citizens with Government Jobs. The motion directs staff to remove citizenship as a requirement for many county positions. 

First, San Francisco removed the requirement to be a US citizen to serve on a school board or commission and now, LA County has removed the citizenship requirement for most county jobs. 

“This is the future Democrats want. Do you think this is fair to OUR citizens? NO!!!! Serious countries don’t hire citizens from another country to help run their government. We need leadership with common sense again.” ~ @robbystarbuck 

Non Citizens should NOT be rewarded with jobs in our government leading our County, City, or States; this decision will only hurt qualified American Citizens who should be first in line for these positions.

The L.A. County Board of Supervisors unanimously approved a motion allowing the county, with a few exceptions, to hire noncitizens to lead county agencies — excluding the chief probation officer — and for any other county jobs where state or federal law doesn't mandate citizenship.

node.text:
Meanwhile American Citizens are being forced to show proof of vaccination in some major cities just to go about your daily lives. This is an outrage. 

Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton on Wednesday slammed President Biden and his administration over the handling of illegal immigrants amid the pandemic, telling Fox News it was “hypocritical” and that “the credibility of the president on COVID is gone.”

Paxton said he had lost all “respect for the president” given he was releasing illegal immigrants into the community while still preaching about the importance of masks and vaccines.

“He is letting all these people in knowing they have COVID. They are being dropped off all over the country. I was talking to some Dallas police officers. They watched … a couple of buses unload in downtown Dallas in the middle of the night. These people just disappeared. Many of them have COVID.

“And to be lectured about masks and vaccines by the administration, to be told when you are out of the country and a US citizen, you can’t come back if you have COVID, is hypocritical.

“I have lost complete respect for the president on the whole COVID issue given the fact that he is allowing people to cross the border and doesn’t seem to care.”

Meanwhile, Fox News’ Tucker Carlson has revealed that a convicted illegal felon had been allowed to remain in the US by Immigration and Customs Enforcement following a request from an Abolish ICE activist.

Citing emails that he obtained, Carlson said ICE Acting Director Tae Johnson had given permission for Marvin Jerezano Pena to remain in the country after being approached by activist Tania Mattos.

Carlson claimed Pena, who has prior convictions for robbery, simple assault and drug charges, was ordered deported in July last year.

“This is what they’re doing as our border has turned into total chaos … our country is being invaded by the rest of the world — not just Mexico, not just Latin America, the whole world — and they’re worried about how they can keep a felon in our country without you knowing about it,” Carlson said, adding that ICE confirmed that Pena was not deported.

node.text:
The Pentagon announcing it will deploy three infantry battalions, or roughly 3,000 troops, to assist with the reduction of American civilians at the U.S. Embassy in Kabul, 

The Pentagon cited a deteriorating security situation in Afghanistan as the reason for the deployment.

There have been an increasing number of reports from the region of Taliban forces seizing more territory as the Biden administration continues the wind down of the U.S. combat mission in Afghanistan.

Trump criticized the Biden administration’s withdrawal in a statement Thursday.

“Had our 2020 Presidential Election not been rigged, and if I were now President, the world would find that our withdrawal from Afghanistan would be a conditions-based withdrawal. I personally had discussions with top Taliban leaders whereby they understood what they are doing now would not have been acceptable,” he said.

“It would have been a much different and much more successful withdrawal, and the Taliban understood that better than anyone. What is going on now is not acceptable. It should have been done much better,” he added.

Kirby insisted the Biden administration would still aim to withdraw U.S. combat forces by the end of August.

node.text:

(*slide 2 sounds like Obama all over again) 

*NOTE: It is increasingly clear that the U.S. departure being handled by senile Joe Biden was so rushed and poorly planned that it will be impossible to evacuate everyone at risk of Taliban reprisal says an opinion by The New Yorker 😳

Afghan government forces are collapsing even faster than U.S. military leaders thought possible just a few months ago when President Joe Biden ordered a full withdrawal. But there's little appetite at the White House, the Pentagon or among the American public for trying to stop the rout and it probably is too late to do so.

Biden has made clear he has no intention of reversing the decision he made last spring, even as the outcome seems to point toward a Taliban takeover. With most U.S. troops now gone and the Taliban accelerating their battlefield gains, American military leaders are not pressing him to change his mind. They know that the only significant option would be for the president to restart the war he already decided to end.

node.text:
If you haven’t heard this radio transmission, please take the time to listen. ⛔️Be cautioned it is hard to listen to.⛔️

The calm voice in the chaos  in Chicago during the incident that occurred on 8/7/2021. Thank you Dispatcher Keith Thornton - The way he took control of this incident and talked to his officers, kept his air completely shut down and clear, set a perimeter within seconds quite possibly is what resulted in the apprehension of the suspects. 

Dispatcher Keith Thornton was fast thinking and took initiative without any direction in the very beginning stages and ran the emergency like an actual incident commander - far beyond the criteria of any dispatcher. 

The world heard you loud and clear and we stand with you. 💙🖤💙🖤💙🖤💙

node.text:
Barry Obama’s maskless, 60th birthday bash was the biggest fuck you to Joe Biden in the history of fuck yous.

What other explanation could there possibly be for Obama holding a maskless, high-profile, elitist soiree just as Slow Joe and his allies in the fake media are on an anti-science, anti-math rampage to terrify us with the China Flu?

Think about it… At the very same time Biden and the discredited CDC and the fake media are ginning up their latest fear campaign, Barack and Michelle Obama put on a Huge Show in front of the whole world by sticking their collective finger directly in the eye of Biden and this fear campaign.

Obama’s maskless soiree not only put the White House on defense, but it also proved Obama doesn’t take this “delta variant” hysteria seriously. But what it really proved is that he doesn’t take Joe Biden seriously. And on both counts, Obama is exactly right.

In fact, we should all hold hands and join Obama’s belligerent campaign to tell Biden, and his fear campaign, fuck you.

This might actually be the first time Barry has done something positive for a country he hates and for the people of this country, who he hates even more.

Honestly, if you think about it, the Obamas sent a great message to America… If you’re vaccinated, this pandemic is over. Don’t listen to the fear merchants. Don’t listen to Joe Biden. Go and live your life.
